        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for information on expression.</p>
            <p>Poor progress of civilisation in South Africa. CD’s doubts and fears about democracy.</p>
            <p>JPMW’s views on glaciation in S. Africa will discredit him unless supported by clearest evidence.</p>
